readable.content: A group of bohemians stroll down the street , one with a shopping cart . A group of four people prance away from the camera , one pushing a shopping cart and another leaping alongside . A group of young people walk down a residential street , one pushing a grocery cart . Four people walking down the street and one is trying to jump in a shopping cart . Four young people walk down a sunny street , one pushing a shopping cart
